 Deputy Governor of Lagos State, Obafemi Hamzat, has apprehended two commercial drivers and their buses for driving against traffic. According to News Agency of Nigeria, the commercial drivers were apprehended at Majidun area of Ikorodu on Saturday The buses with registration numbers FKJ 704 XK and FKJ 864 XV, were driving inward Ikorodu using the outward Ikorodu Lane. The two buses and drivers were handed over to the Divisional Police Officer at Owode Onirin Police Station for necessary action.